to a desert island ?

167
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:34,760
What's the biggest difference
between the US and Canada ?

168
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:38,240
What's the biggest difference between
America and Scotland ?

169
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,560
